{"tid":220273,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"曼波雪條真係好高質","createTime":"2017-04-27T23:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T00:47:43.000Z","uid":17343,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06980d10cd92dd9b9665e174d0e651ac1ffe9254","tid":220273,"uid":17343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T23:11:46.000Z","msg":"曼波把聲真係好好聽 我直情Down 嗮佢D歌落電話 日日聽<br />\n<br />\n可惜既係曼波好多作品都係日文 <br />\n<br />\n柒柒既我聽唔明 淨系聽演繹 唔咁亂推薦<br />\n<br />\n下面推薦下D廣東話作品 希望多D巴打可以聽到曼波咁好聽既聲線啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 非打手 非曼波分身 純fans<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咁多 比Link最實際 <br />\n<br />\n曼波youtube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/shiroshiro615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fshiroshiro615&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=fc32af20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/shiroshiro615</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chrishiro2525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchrishiro2525&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=477a5b12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chrishiro2525</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《一個回眸》原：明目張膽</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n挽歌巴打既詞 講雷姆做兵<br />\n加上曼波沉沉地既聲線<br />\n真係聽到好sad <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yL0RqaICjB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyL0RqaICjB8&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=aa7b7cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yL0RqaICjB8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《一聲再見》原：Secret Base</span></strong><br />\n未聞花名首主題曲廣東話版 <br />\n我就真心覺得呢個版本仲好聽過日文原版啦<br />\n<br />\n<em>抬著臉只得灰色天空 空中呼呼北風<br />\n風裡肆意放縱 眼神迷濛<br />\n而那句我很喜歡尚未道出<br />\n一轉身怎麼失去了影蹤</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x2XmB1cLv4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx2XmB1cLv4w&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=658827ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x2XmB1cLv4w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>字花 cover </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n比起原版聽落舒服D 柔和D 聽落好舒服 好似慢慢講緊故事咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yTpumQcbIJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyTpumQcbIJE&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=02ac1ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yTpumQcbIJE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">囍帖街cover </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n曼波自己做既Cover 好好聽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o2-scKf_V1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do2-scKf_V1I&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=9f44e83a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o2-scKf_V1I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黑洞</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我記得曼波係直播唱過 果陣已經覺得好好聽 呢排發現原來SoundCloud有 <br />\n興奮到<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/chrishiro_manball/neyrewmp27ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fchrishiro_manball%2Fneyrewmp27ac&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4829eb91\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/chrishiro_manball/neyrewmp27ac</a>"},{"pid":"a75975f7bab86f892388af2b868b11670d32c16d","tid":220273,"uid":17343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:05:41.000Z","msg":"無人鍾意曼波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7480c9d7c20471b31f4f9713e6f1bac636c8dbb4","tid":220273,"uid":173